oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Pickard Family Kolorbak Commercial Takes
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is of Bub Pickard (musician) of the Pickard Family (musical group) performing a number of Kolorbak commercial takes. The recording is from of an unidentified date. The recording was recorded in Mexico.
